ay along the curving roadway, large white capital letters appear across the middle of the picture: “PLYMOUTH!” The car grows smaller ahead on the road, with trees and shoreline behind it. The bold “PLYMOUTH!” text remains centered over the moving road scene. Near the end, the text changes to read “YOUR” above, “PLYMOUTH!” in large letters across the center, and “DEALER” below, all in white block capitals, while the road stretches into the distance.",
